'''庫內魯鐵路事故'''為發生於2017年1月21日的鐵路事故，一列車次18448的{{tsl|en|Hirakhand express||希拉克漢德列車}}由[[贾格达尔普尔|贾格达尔普尔]]駛往[[布巴内什瓦尔|布巴内什瓦尔]]，行經[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]{{tsl|en|Kuneru||庫內魯}}時[[脫軌|脫軌]]，造成41人死亡，68人受傷，當時列車上乘客約600人<ref name="time">{{cite news |title=Investigation into India Train Crash Launched as Death Toll Rises to 41 |url=http://time.com/4642945/india-train-crash-andhra-pradesh/ |date=23 January 2017 |work=Time |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2021-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508052124/https://time.com/4642945/india-train-crash-andhra-pradesh/ }}</ref>。

== 事故 ==
事發列車為[[柴油機車|柴油機車]]牽引9輛[[鐵路客車|鐵路客車]]，於當地時間晚間11點左右脫軌<ref name="1:">{{cite news |date=2017-01-22 |title=Jagdalpur-Bhubaneswar Hirakhand Express derails LIVE updates: 39 dead, Railways suspect sabotage; Suresh Prabhu meets victims’ family |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/india/jagdalpur-bhubaneswar-hirakhand-express-derailment-live-updates-dead-several-injured-rescue-ops-underway-4485949/ |newspaper=The Indian Express |location=New Delhi |access-date=2017-01-22 |archive-date=2021-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006090732/https://indianexpress.com/article/india/jagdalpur-bhubaneswar-hirakhand-express-derailment-live-updates-dead-several-injured-rescue-ops-underway-4485949/ }}</ref>，3輛客車完全脫離軌道<ref name="reuters">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-india-crash-idUSKBN15604D?il=0|title=At least 39 killed as Indian train derails|agency=Reuters|date=22 January 2017|accessdate=23 January 2017|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316091823/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-india-crash-idUSKBN15604D?il=0}}</ref>，另有一些客車撞擊其他軌道的[[鐵路貨車|鐵路貨車]]<ref name="aj">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/01/dozens-killed-train-derails-southern-india-170122070105157.html|title=Dozens killed after train derails in southern India|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=22 January 2017|accessdate=23 January 2017|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225190158/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/01/dozens-killed-train-derails-southern-india-170122070105157.html}}</ref>，主管當局表示有部分傷亡係因脫軌後，乘客欲逃生時踩踏而造成<ref name="nyt">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/22/world/asia/india-train-hirakhand-express.html?ref=world|title=Train Derails in Southern India, Killing Dozens|work=The New York Times|date=22 January 2017|accessdate=23 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922181223/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/22/world/asia/india-train-hirakhand-express.html?ref=world}}</ref>，救援人員迅速趕到事發現場進行救援<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-38708477|title=India Andhra Pradesh train crash leaves 39 dead and scores injured|date=2017-01-22|newspaper=BBC News|language=en-GB|access-date=2017-01-25|archive-date=2022-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220219022040/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-38708477}}</ref>。

